    "The multiclass classification issue was modeled using a Conv1d model.",
    "73 \"artefact\" samples were accurately identified as belonging to the \"artefact\" class.",
    "No instances of \"artefact\" being incorrectly categorized as another category (false positives) were found.",
    "Furthermore, no samples from other classes were incorrectly labeled as \"artefact' (false negatives).",
    "Twenty \"exstole\" samples were authentic (true positives), meaning the class was correctly identified."
